title.rendered: OFFROAD ANIMAL PREDATOR BULLBAR – ISUZU D-MAX (2021+)

content.rendered:
OFFROAD ANIMAL PREDATOR BULLBAR TO ISUZU D-MAX (2021+)

Offroad Animal Predator bullbar to suit Isuzu D-MAX (2021+) available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Features of the pictured bullbar include;

  • ADR compliant
  • Airbag compatible
  • Bumper replacement, with no cutting of bumper
  • Optional top hoop – Stealth hoop which takes up to a 22″ LED light bar single row, or 2″ round tube
  • Welded one piece bar with welded wing supports
  • Only sits 150-160mm out from front of grill
  • Zinc plated then powder coated Matte black
  • Hi lift jacking points included
  • Suits most low mount winches
  • Works with factory fog lights
  • Can be colour coded to vehicle
  • Standard 20mm steel recovery points included as part of mount
  • Only adds 130mm to front of vehicle

PLEASE NOTE: Price of bullbar includes freight to Automax 4×4 in Coffs Harbour. Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order. 

CLICK HERE to view the range of products available for your Isuzu D-MAX!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
